    <item nodeId="node-1069">
        <command xml:space="preserve">frotz</command>
        <result xml:space="preserve">Behold! Now the room is lit!

Dark Corner
Now that it's light, you see that this room is little more than a nook at the top of a narrow stair. It looks like you can just squeeze through a tight crack to the north.

Smoky tendrils float through the room. You can just make out a message in them: "\above Glass Maze is Dark Corner, which is dark"

&gt;</result>
