        <result xml:space="preserve">
Treasure Room
The brillliance of this room is staggering, the light reflecting from a million coins and refracting through a thousand jewels. But you are not here for wealth, you are here for wisdom.

A narrow crack leads south.

You can see a jewel-encrusted book here.

&gt;</result>
